>这篇帖子&lt;/a>&lt;/p>
&lt;p>&lt;img src="https://blog.kmtea.eu/p/221227-pve-openwrt/img/21-forum.jpg"
width="1077"
height="1280"
srcset="https://blog.kmtea.eu/p/221227-pve-openwrt/img/21-forum_huc3b7e49d830a4409ff1c8a990966c57c_49369_480x0_resize_q75_box.jpg 480w, https://blog.kmtea.eu/p/221227-pve-openwrt/img/21-forum_huc3b7e49d830a4409ff1c8a990966c57c_49369_1024x0_resize_q75_box.jpg 1024w"
loading="lazy"
alt="Solution"
class="gallery-image"
data-flex-grow="84"
data-flex-basis="201px"
>&lt;/p>
